==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Misinform
<hw>Mis`in*form"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To give untrue
information to; to inform wrongly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misinform</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Misinform
<hw>Mis`in*form"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To give untrue information;
(with <xex>against</xex>) to calumniate.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bp. Montagu.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misinformant</ent>⟦br⟧
